PrecisRegulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (LIGHTING AND RETROREFLECTIVE DEVICES) which make minor revisions to sections 108 and 108.1 to reflect the recent amendments made to Department of Transport Technical Standards Document No. 108 which now allows for the installation of visually-optically aimable (VOA) headlamps.

precis:
Regulations Amending the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (LIGHTING AND
RETROREFLECTIVE DEVICES) which make minor revisions to sections 108 and
108.1 to reflect the recent amendments made to Department of Transport
Technical Standards Document No. 108 which now allows for the installation
of visually-optically aimable (VOA) headlamps.
